snippet.title: The Lord of the Rings: Return to Moria™ - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The first gameplay trailer for The Lord of the Rings: Return to Moria, the only survival crafting game set in the Fourth Age of Middle-earth™, the iconic fantasy world created by J.R.R. Tolkien

Find out more at www.ReturnToMoria.com
